-- new foundational pillar: covariance, gauge invariance, and partial
-- superselection rules.  Defines:
--   • `IsUnitaryRep U` — packaging Prop for a unitary representation.
--   • `IsGCovariant U A` — `U g · A · (U g)† = A` for all g ∈ G.
--   • `twirl U A` — finite-group average  (1/|G|) Σ_g U g · A · (U g)†,
--     the Banach projector onto the G-covariant subspace.
